hwt.name: (sda_chk & (~(sig_ & sig_) | (sig_ & sig_) | (sig_ & sig_)) & (~sda_t)) | ((~lastSda) & ((sig_ & sig_) | (sig_ & sig_) | (sig_ & sig_)) & ((sig_ & sig_) | (sig_ & sig_) | (sig_ & sig_)) & (~cmd_stop))
(~lastSda) & ((sig_ & sig_) | (sig_ & sig_) | (sig_ & sig_)) & ((sig_ & sig_) | (sig_ & sig_) | (sig_ & sig_)) & (~cmd_stop)
(~lastSda) & ((sig_ & sig_) | (sig_ & sig_) | (sig_ & sig_)) & ((sig_ & sig_) | (sig_ & sig_) | (sig_ & sig_))

hwt.bodyText:
If(filter_clk_cntr._eq(0x0),
    sda_filter1_next(Concat(sig_, sig_)),
    scl_filter1_next(Concat(sig_, sig_)),
).Else(
    sda_filter1_next(sda_filter1),
    scl_filter1_next(scl_filter1),
)

If((clk)._onRisingEdge(),
    If(rst_n._eq(0x0),
        stateClkEn(0x1),
        st(stT.idle),
        slave_wait(0x0),
        sda_t(0x0),
        sda_filter1(0x7),
        sda_filter0(0x0),
        sda_chk(0x0),
        scl_t(0x0),
        scl_filter1(0x7),
        scl_filter0(0x0),
        lastSda(0x1),
        lastScl(0x1),
        filter_clk_cntr(clk_cnt_initVal),
        doutReg(0x0),
        delayedScl_t(0x1),
        cmd_stop(0x0),
        clkCntr((clk_cnt_initVal)._reinterpret_cast(Bits(16, signed=False, forceVector=True))),
        al(0x0),
    ).Else(
        stateClkEn(stateClkEn_next),
        st(st_next),
        slave_wait(slave_wait_next),
        sda_t(sda_t_next),
        sda_filter1(sda_filter1_next),
        sda_filter0(sda_filter0_next),
        sda_chk(sda_chk_next),
        scl_t(scl_t_next),
        scl_filter1(scl_filter1_next),
        scl_filter0(scl_filter0_next),
        lastSda(lastSda_next),
        lastScl(lastScl_next),
        filter_clk_cntr(filter_clk_cntr_next),
        doutReg(doutReg_next),
        delayedScl_t(delayedScl_t_next),
        cmd_stop(cmd_stop_next),
        clkCntr(clkCntr_next),
        al(al_next),
    ),
)
